{"tid":354171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重案組探員到興德學校搜證","createTime":"2017-08-10T08:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T11:13:30.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6df5f77ecb2fef57461cfbf555cbf07d1b5d1fac","tid":354171,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:07:28.000Z","msg":"屯門興德學校涉以「影子學生」騙取教育局津貼事件愈鬧愈大，當中更懷疑牽涉偽造文件。現場消息指，5名重案組探員於下午3時30分，抵達興德學校搜證。<br />\n<br />\n教育局早前表示，經調查後發現，屯門興德學校有「影子學生」問題，即部分學生無上學和考試，但仍然能升班。教育局已向該校校長陳章萍發出的警告信，局方在信中提出5宗嚴重違規及異常情況指控，直指陳章萍處理校內事務時有違校長應有的專業操守，嚴重違反《香港教育專業守則》及教育局根據《教育條例》發出的指示。<br />\n<br />\n就連串指控，陳章萍周二(8日)在記者會上哭訴，稱感到委屈，強調多年來為學校克盡己任，她又質疑事件是有組織、有預謀的部署。"},{"pid":"706f0f43793e7e65c2aaabca7889567fd771fd03","tid":354171,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b88e9cc9831cc1cd8c354055c9f9ca77e3386df","tid":354171,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"個組織就係警察"},{"pid":"92ba9b32fc47b56fa18a707603a8e5347d64321f","tid":354171,"uid":13260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:30:00.000Z","msg":"黑鬥黑"},{"pid":"505e574f18088b2672f4ff873a9e817a0a42fa8f","tid":354171,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:31:13.000Z","msg":"應該有班同學係年年都留班，去到六年級都唔會升中學。<br />\n<br />\n咁就年年都有準貼。"},{"pid":"83618c0cf4d282846b3b4283af2ea5d8fd630c1a","tid":354171,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底一日要食幾多西餅先可以咁肥"},{"pid":"f86e6e98b1b8524827ca934839c1b78f7cb368ad","tid":354171,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:14:31.000Z","msg":"[肥婆掉眼淚]興德校歌最新試唱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/354255/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/354255/page/1?ref=web</a>"},{"pid":"8b6d6f8a9167611d2381813ec04c9ce8538a8a53","tid":354171,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T11:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[肥婆掉眼淚]興德校歌最新試唱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/354255/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/354255/page/1?ref=web</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}